<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Nobody can, nor should they be able to, force you to use your body to sustain another life.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I answered the &quot;force&quot; thing already. You never addressed what I said. Now you use it to validate your argument. Intresting. <br>
<br>
I'll humor this flawed logic for a bit though, since its all you will seemingly respond to.<br>
